description: This quiz is intended for users familiar with Google Analytics, a tool for measuring website, app, digital and offline data to gain customer insights. The questions are similar to the certification test, but this quiz is designed to be a fun game for data nerds who want to show off their smarts. Disclaimer: This quiz is not produced or endorsed by Google or the Google Analytics product team.

shortDescription: Test your Google Analytics knowledge with 5ft of Dynamite's Unofficial Google Analytics Quiz, a trivia game based on the Google Analytics platform.
